</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="410ED7514203895BFF755C59FBC2C735" blockId="4.[225,1436,1814,1919]" pageId="4" pageNumber="14">
Genus of the subfamily 
<taxonomicName id="86B1ACD24203895BFE635C59FD59C77C" authorityName="Korn" authorityYear="2002" box="[501,669,1814,1840]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Ponticeratidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ammonoidea" pageId="4" pageNumber="14" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Ponticeratinae">Ponticeratinae</taxonomicName>
with extremely discoidal, subevolute conch. Without ventrolateral grooves. Suture line with relatively narrow external lobe, very low median saddle, very small E2 lobe, shallow and rounded lateral lobe. Suture line formula (E 
<subScript id="DD35D5144203895BFCE15C3EFC44C733" attach="left" box="[887,896,1905,1919]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="14">2</subScript>
E 
<subScript id="DD35D5144203895BFC0F5C3EFC66C733" attach="left" box="[921,930,1905,1919]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="14">1</subScript>
E 
<subScript id="DD35D5144203895BFC2D5C3EFC00C733" attach="left" box="[955,964,1905,1919]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="14">2</subScript>
) L: I.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
